ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  "sparql_query": "PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\n\\nSELECT ?zone ?zoneLabel ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint\\nWHERE {\\n  # zones\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n  OPTIONAL { ?zone rdfs:label ?zoneLabel }\\n  # properties attached to the zone\\n  ?zone s223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  # property label\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel }\\n  # non‑writable filter (either absent or explicit false)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:writable ?writable }\\n  FILTER ( !BOUND(?writable) || ?writable = false )\\n  # ALC endpoint (generic Brick endpoint)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint }\\n  # MPC endpoint (specific Brick MPC name)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone ?propLabel"\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 21, 19, 15, 51, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
